# SKELETRON

**Action:** Color in each pole with a rainbow sequence red, orange, yellow, green, blue, purple.  Draw in a hanging [TRASH ROBOT](scrolls/trashrobot) flag.  Go find someone who knows Skeletron at a [TRASH STATION](scrolls/trashstation) and build a structure.
 
![](https://i.imgur.com/QrmCzrS.png)
![](https://i.imgur.com/QTjJh0w.jpg)
![](https://i.imgur.com/Qg40z9U.png)
![](https://i.imgur.com/1C9CvwP.jpg)

6 foot bamboo poles, wrapped in rainbow duct tape, quarter inch holes drilled at ends and middle, tied with trash ties, which are 18 inch sections of nylon parachute cord with burned ends.

